microphone jacks were unified into one and Apple introduced a “MagSafe 2” power connection. They even took the time to design special fans with a-symmetrical blade arrangements so the laptop is quieter. This all translates into one bad ass laptop that has skyrocketed to the top of my to-do list.\r\n\r\nWWDC and E3 were pretty awesome, but that’s about all that happened in the past two weeks, though I am pretty positive I missed something somewhere.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSource: <strong><em>MacRumorsLive</em></strong>', 'The Past Two Weeks: E3 & WWDC [WWDC Edition]', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '92-revision-3', '', '', '2012-06-15 03:05:50', '2012-06-15 03:05:50', '', 92, 'http://www.slushie.me/2012/97/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
