(138, 2, '2012-06-14 21:50:42', '2012-06-14 21:50:42', 'Just two hundred years ago battles waged on even after the war was finished.\r\n\r\nLess than a century from today the first audio broadcast echoed through waves in the air and crackled out of speakers.\r\n\r\nThen, in homes across America, dark rooms were illuminated by moving pictures and sound across black and white screens.\r\n\r\nSeemingly unending information now rests at our fingertips.\r\n\r\nMedia is constantly changing. It marches forward every second of every minute. Days. Months. Years. There is no turning back the clock on our dynamic world.\r\n\r\nWe are pleased to present the voices of writers from across the nation (and one day the globe). Voices that speak through podcasts, videos and blogs.\r\n\r\nWelcome to Slushie.\r\n\r\nHave the everything blend.', 'A Letter from the Management', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '64-revision-8', '', '', '2012-06-14 21:50:42', '2012-06-14 21:50:42', '', 64, 'http://www.slushie.me/2012/138/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
