(313, 5, '2012-12-06 13:59:24', '2012-12-06 18:59:24', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-315" alt="" src="http://www.slushie.me/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/troika33.jpg" width="1440" height="900" />\r\n\r\nMashing sensation and DJ, Troika, has recently begun to get popularity amongst the community in Baltimore, the Eastern coast of the United States, and some European countries. DJ Troika, a 17-year-old high school student at Gilman high school, has taken the first step in becoming a known DJ; he has officially come out with his first EP. The Kaleidoscope EP is a 5 song collection of his newest tracks. DJ Troika has more than 24 thousand plays all together on his SoundCloud page. Music blogs from all around the world are beginning to post his mashes and original masterpieces.\r\n\r\nI am fortunate enough to know Troika personally and he was willing to answer some questions specifically for Slushie:\r\n\r\n<strong>Slushie</strong>: Where are you getting recognition?\r\n<strong>Troika</strong>: I''ve gotten write-ups for the Kaleidoscope EP from DML.fm, SoSimpull, The Kollection, and a major 8tracks playlist maker called DopeStephan has included a few tracks in his playlist.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slushie</strong>: What caused you to take up DJ’ing?\r\n<strong>Troika</strong>: As a kid, I was a little brat about taking up an instrument, and I dropped trombone after 8th grade. I felt a bit empty because I didn''t have any musical outlet, so I took up production and DJing to fill the void.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slushie</strong>: As most of us would agree, Troika is a sick name, what exactly is a Troika?\r\n<strong>Troika</strong>: A troika is a Russian chariot drawn by three horses. The story behind why I chose the name is because I was going to be working with two other people I knew, but they all abandoned the project, and I took it up solo.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slushie</strong>: What is your main goal as a DJ and how big do you want to get?\r\n<strong>Troika</strong>: At the moment, my goals are undetermined. The only thing <em>I DO</em> know is that I want to play at some decently large festival sometime during 2013. What music will I make in the future? It''s anyone''s guess. And if I get big from it, I won''t reject that. Let the people decide.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slushie</strong>: Have you ever been recognized outside of Gilman, your high school?\r\n<strong>Troika</strong>: The thing about the Gilman community is that they think that I''m a joke. That''s fine. If anything, that''s a gimmick, and when I came out with the EP, people were very impressed. Now, to get back to your question. There''s been a surge of likes to my Facebook page, and apparently, I make good music, so yes. People recognize me.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slushie</strong>: What is the biggest venue you’ve performed at?\r\n<strong>Troika</strong>: The biggest venue I''ve performed at is at the fairgrounds in York, PA. There were about 2000 people. It was pretty cool.\r\n\r\n<strong>Slushie</strong>: Is this your first time being interviewed for a blog?\r\n<strong>Troika</strong>: For the most part, yeah.\r\n\r\nDJ Troika has mixes of different lengths and genres of music. On iTunes, Troika has an hour-long podcast, called the <a title="Troikast" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/the-troikast/id558299838?mt=2" target="_blank">Troikast</a>,(because Troika is applying to colleges, the podcast is on hold), and on <a title="Troika Soundcloud" href="https://soundcloud.com/troikamash" target="_blank">SoundCloud</a>, the best place to find his music, is where he posts the majority of his music.\r\n\r\nSome of my favorite works by Troika include the hour-long podcast on <a title="Troikast" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/the-troikast/id558299838?mt=2" target="_blank">iTunes</a>, his <a title="Steez Mix" href="https://soundcloud.com/troikamash/troika-steez-mix" target="_blank">Troika Steez Mix</a>, and his <a title="EP" href="https://soundcloud.com/troikamash/sets/kaleidoscope-ep-1">Kaleidoscope EP</a>.\r\n\r\nFor updates on his music and other new albums check out his <a href="https://www.facebook.com/troikamash?fref=ts">Facebook Page</a>.', 'DJ Troika ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dj-troika', '', '', '2013-01-12 19:00:16', '2013-01-13 00:00:16', '', 0, 'http://www.slushie.me/?p=313', 0, 'post', '', 0),
