(480, 8, '2013-02-25 18:05:20', '2013-02-25 23:05:20', '<p style="text-align: left;">For your March viewing pleasure we have an interesting slate of movies in the works. The clear front runner in this group is Dead Man Down. <a href="http://www.slushie.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/dead-mand-down.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-482 aligncenter" alt="dead mand down" src="http://www.slushie.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/dead-mand-down.jpg" width="275" height="183" /></a>An action, thriller coming out on March 8th. The film revolves around two strangers and their mutual desire for revenge. Check out the trailer <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xGr0vUe41vM">here</a>. It''s definitely on my list of films to watch. Coming out on the same day, is Oz The Great and Powerful. This is a prequel to The Wizard of Oz, starring James Franco and Mila Kunis. It tells the story of the wizard before he meets Dorothy. Certainly an interesting plot. Here is the trailer for it as <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_1NGnVLDPog">well</a>. If you thought that movie was star studded however just take a look at G.I. Joe: Retaliation. With more stars than you can shake a stick at, the sequel to the 2009 Joe movie looks poised to take box office supremacy. The movie is centered around the team''s conflict with Cobra along with a new threat coming from within the government. Coming to <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9liN57pFPQ">theaters</a> March 29th. Other cools movies coming out in the coming month include, <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iM58i51jwRA">21 and Over</a>, <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p_L7URIZNhQ">Day of the Falcon</a>, and <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ng9rjC8MOgU">Jack the Giant Slayer</a>. Enjoy March moviegoers it''s going to be a good one.</p>', 'What''s Coming Up! March Edition.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'whats-coming-up-march-edition', '', '', '2013-02-25 18:13:10', '2013-02-25 23:13:10', '', 0, 'http://www.slushie.me/?p=480', 0, 'post', '', 0),
